thread.title_full: Fast Cover Travel Insurance reviewed by Bryce Allen

author: Bryce Allen
title: Bryce Allen
text: Was super quick and easy to set up. Talked through with Fast Cover over the phone to gain a better understanding of what was covered and what was needed if i had to claim. Very informative and helpful, here's hoping for a claim free trip!
